<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ yé hé huá qiú nǐ shè miǎn, yīn wèi yǎ gè wēi ruò.
 zhǔ yé hé huá qiú nǐ zhǐ xī, yīn wèi yǎ gè wēi ruò.
 tā zěn néng zhàn lì de zhù ne, qiú nǐ bù yào zé dǎ.
 tā zěn néng zhàn lì de zhù ne, qiú nǐ dà shī ēn huì.</lyrics>
